<p>Before EF7 I used the snipet below to remove conventions:</p>  <pre><code>protected override void OnModelCreating(DbModelBuilder builder) {       builder.Conventions.Remove&lt;NavigationPropertyNameForeignKeyDiscoveryConvention&gt;();       builder.Conventions.Remove&lt;PrimaryKeyNameForeignKeyDiscoveryConvention&gt;();       builder.Conventions.Remove&lt;PluralizingTableNameConvention&gt;();       builder.Conventions.Remove&lt;PrimaryKeyNameForeignKeyDiscoveryConvention&gt;();       builder.Conventions.Remove&lt;TypeNameForeignKeyDiscoveryConvention&gt;(); } </code></pre>  <p>How do we achieve the same result on Entity Framework 7?</p>